ings demonstrate the importance of\nunderstanding in detail multi-band physics and electrostatic effects in the\ncontext of the ongoing search for Majorana modes in\nsemiconductor-superconductor heterostructures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Feb 2019 18:57:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-11"}
