e individual is not under active surveillance by the authorities, but\nthe individual's friends/associates are, then the individual planning the\nattack can be uniquely identified. We apply our techniques on various\nreal-world terror network datasets and show the effectiveness of our approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Feb 2019 20:40:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-11"}
